  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0f5fc430403e19d4f88a66d2829b79f7, type: 3}
  description: "Gia Lai l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn
    \u1EDF mi\u1EC1n Trung c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh
    l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Pleiku. Gia Lai n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi c\u1EA3nh
    quan thi\xEAn nhi\xEAn h\xF9ng v\u0129 nh\u01B0 Bi\u1EC3n H\u1ED3 (T\u2019N\u01B0ng)
    c\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng c\xE1nh r\u1EEBng v\xE0 cao nguy\xEAn r\u1ED9ng l\u1EDBn.
    Ngo\xE0i ra, t\u1EC9nh c\xF2n mang \u0111\u1EADm b\u1EA3n s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a
    c\u1EE7a c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn nh\u01B0 Ba Na, Jrai v\u1EDBi
    nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng v\xE0 kh\xF4ng gian v\u0103n
    h\xF3a c\u1ED3ng chi\xEAng \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 12/6/2025, theo Ngh\u1ECB quy\u1EBFt s\u1ED1 202/2025/QH15,
    t\u1EC9nh B\xECnh \u0110\u1ECBnh v\xE0 Gia Lai s\xE1p nh\u1EADp th\xE0nh t\u1EC9nh
    Gia Lai (m\u1EDBi), t\u1EA1o ra \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh l\u1EDBn
    v\u1EDBi di\u1EC7n t\xEDch h\u01A1n 21.576 km\xB2 v\xE0 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 h\u01A1n
    3,58 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. T\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 135 \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB
    h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh c\u1EA5p x\xE3, trung t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t
    t\u1EA1i B\xECnh \u0110\u1ECBnh, trong khi Pleiku l\xE0 c\u01A1 s\u1EDF 2."
